{"tid":1973152,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"俄一周逾千確診 普京響警號","createTime":"2020-04-15T04:16:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T04:38:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c3d9f704565b624616c58394d2023d81241ef8a7","tid":1973152,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T04:16:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200415/MD6D5MKVMB5ELURGVZIZ2KBZUQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200415%2FMD6D5MKVMB5ELURGVZIZ2KBZUQ%2F&d=kRIfmd%2Br1GQrfPRU1wEKQP2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=7d7c0d85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200415%2FMD6D5MKVMB5ELURGVZIZ2KBZUQ%2F&h=da178ec1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200415/MD6D5MKVMB5ELURGVZIZ2KBZUQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n俄一周逾千確診 普京響警號<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200415/large/1586880553_cbb6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200415%2Flarge%2F1586880553_cbb6.gif&h=d32c3530&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n普京警告國家會踏入關鍵的抗疫階段，促官員不能鬆懈。歐新社<br />\n<br />\n有英國倫敦帝國學院專家指，歐洲多國武漢肺炎疫情看來已到達高峯，但憂慮會輪到拉丁美洲、非洲與東南亞地區的疫情升溫，又尤其擔心俄羅斯情況。俄國過去一周每天皆見逾千宗確診個案增長，累計逾兩萬人確診，總統普京警告官員要為「非常情況」作準備。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：拒設失業援助金 籲申請綜援<br />\n<br />\n或要求軍人協助<br />\n<br />\n倫敦帝國學院呼吸系統科教授約翰斯頓認為，法國、德國、西班牙、意大利等歐洲國家的疫情應該已到高峯，但俄國的狀況仍惹他憂心。俄國昨累計21,102人確診，170人不治。普京前天也警告，當地情況「每天都在改變，但不幸地並非好的改變」，未來數周更會迎來「關鍵」時刻。他敦促官員要為所有情況做足準備，如國家有需要也會要求軍人協助。<br />\n<br />\n俄國曾經派專機送抗疫物資到美國與意大利等地，但普京前天承認，國家也面臨防護裝備短缺問題，「我們要採取額外措施去填補短缺」。外長拉夫羅夫就透露，美國總統特朗普向普京說美國已準備好送一批物資到俄國。<br />\n<br />\n疫情最為嚴峻的莫斯科和其他數個地區採取了封城措施，民眾除購買食物、倒垃圾、尋求緊急醫療協助或必須上班外，不得出門。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社"},{"pid":"f898a66aa1b6ba30d5ecfe805682a91338f8039b","tid":1973152,"uid":245065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T04:17:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f5cb1a0e4542601c17db2648216108f0f94b0c49","tid":1973152,"uid":185656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T04:24:10.000Z","msg":"徵用大連港做隔離營啦"},{"pid":"41d9d4b94ef4519b9c7536ab24519c644dc7cf64","tid":1973152,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T04:25:08.000Z","msg":"Bolly鮮：俄羅斯病毒"},{"pid":"626c557bf7b80066522ff8b84a9d068525172b7a","tid":1973152,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T04:25:53.000Z","msg":"一個支拿病就搞到兄弟反目 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64bed76014baf962606adccd777425d64cd91099","tid":1973152,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T04:26:08.000Z","msg":"契哥收到契弟份回禮了"},{"pid":"77d073b9f6e7d2339e4d71a298f5a9e9d1478032","tid":1973152,"uid":103981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64bed76014baf962606adccd777425d64cd91099","tid":1973152,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T04:26:08.000Z","msg":"契哥收到契弟份回禮了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T04:38:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/02/18/99/7482185.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F02%2F18%2F99%2F7482185.jpg&h=c5863d04&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}